      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor door dings, and the interior upholstery exhibits moderate wear and some staining. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but it will eventually need attention for a slow oil leak and some suspension creaks. It is a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a few imperfections.",
