    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of unparalleled caliber, preserved in exemplary condition. This specimen retains its original showroom luster, featuring an impeccable exterior finish and an interior devoid of wear. Every mechanical system has been vetted to ensure it operates with the precision and reliability expected of a top-tier motorcar. This offering represents a rare opportunity for the sophisticated collector or driver to acquire a vehicle maintained to the most exacting standards of excellence.",
