    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always garage-kept, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019ve been looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for the road, this is the one. You really have to see it in person to believe how clean it is. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
